author: dgraham
msg: Added 1.2 struts-config.dtd.  This is a copy of the 1.1 DTD except that
the <data-source> "type" attribute is now required because Struts will
not supply a default DataSource implementation.

author: dgraham
msg: Can't use super.hashCode() when value is null because it breaks the
equals() contract.  Just use a constant number instead.
